title: Are you up for a challenge? This is going to be fun!
description:
You all have BLOWN US AWAY this week!! I am praying that each of you in your places, building deeper relationships with the people around you could change everything. We have some HUGE things coming in just over a week so make sure you have your copy of the book, subscribe to the show, and text a few people to do this next season with together.

GET YOUR COPY OF FIND YOUR PEOPLE: findyourpeoplebook.com
